To draw a circle on a HTML canvas, you can use the `arc()` method. Here is some code, which may provide you an understanding of how it works:

```javascript
const canvas = document.getElementById('canvas'); // note that you will have to use your own canvas
const context = canvas.getContext('2d');
const x = 100; // x-coordinate, you can set it up
const y = 100; // y-coordinate, you can set it up too
